   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:id="Fr005.TEXT">
            <p>
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                     <seg rendition="#u">Omar Khayyam.</seg>
                     <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
                     <space dim="vertical" quantity="1" unit="minims" />
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                     <seg rendition="#i #center">Omar Khayyam</seg><lb />
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">
                     OMAR KHAYYAM
                     <space dim="vertical" quantity="1" unit="minims" />
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC" />
               </app>
        
        </p><p> O
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">tedio</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">tédio</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               de Khayyam não é o
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">tedio</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">tédio</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               de quem não sabe
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               o que faça, porque na verdade nada
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">póde</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">pode</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               ou sabe fazer.
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               Esse é o
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">tedio</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">tédio</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               dos que nasceram mortos, e dos que legi
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
               timamente se orientam para a
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">morphina</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">morfina</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               ou a
           <app type="orthographic">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">cocaina</rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">cocaína</rdg>
               </app>
               . É
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               mais profundo e mais nobre o
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">tedio</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">tédio</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               do
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">sabio</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">sábio</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               persa. É o
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">tedio</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">tédio</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               de quem pensou claramente e viu que tudo era ob
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
               scuro; de quem mediu todas as religiões e todas as
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                        phi
                        <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
                        losophias
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">filosofias</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               e depois disse, como Salomão: "Vi que tudo
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               era vaidade e
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">afflicções</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">aflições</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               de
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">animo"</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">ânimo"</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               <app>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 "><subst><del rendition="overtyped">.</del><add place="inline">,</add></subst></rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">,</rdg>       
               </app>
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                     <del rend="overtyped">O sabio, porém, foi</del>
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z" />
               </app>
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                     <del rend="overtyped">mais longe</del>
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z" />
               </app>
               ou como, ao despedir-se do poder e do mundo,
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               outro rei, que era imperador,
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">nelle</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">nele</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               ,
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                     <seg rendition="#u">Septimio Severo</seg></rdg>
               </app>
               <app type="style">
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">Septimio</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">Septímio</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               <app type="style">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">Severo</rdg>
               </app>
               :
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               <app type="style">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">Omnia fui, nihil</rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">"Omnia fui, nihil</rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">
                     <seg rendition="#i">Omnia fui, nihil</seg>
                  </rdg>
               </app>
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="substantive">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">........,</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">......</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">
                        <seg rendition="#i">[expedit].</seg>
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">
                        <seg rendition="#i">expedit.</seg>
                     </rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               "Fui tudo; nada vale a pena".
               <app type="style">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="minims" quantity="1" />
                  </rdg>
               </app>
            </p>
            <p>
               A vida, disse Tarde, é a busca do
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                        impossivel
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">impossível</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                        atra
                        <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
                        vez
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">através</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               do
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">inutil</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">inútil</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               ; assim diria, se o houvesse dito, Omar
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               Khayyam.
               <app type="style">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C                                 #Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="minims" quantity="1" />
                  </rdg>
               </app>
            </p>
            <p>
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">De ahi</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">Daí</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               a
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">insistencia</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">insistência</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               do persa no uso do vinho. Bebe!
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               Bebe! é toda a sua
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">philosophia</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">filosofia</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">practica</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">prática</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               . Não é o beber da
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               alegria, que bebe porque mais se alegre, porque mais seja
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">ella</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">ela</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               mesma. Não é o beber do desespero, que bebe para es
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
               quecer, para ser menos
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">elle</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">ele</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               mesmo. Ao vinho junta a ale
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
               gria
               <app type="punctuation">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C" />
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">,</rdg>
               </app>
               a acção e o amor; e
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">ha</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">há</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               que reparar que não
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">ha</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">há</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               em
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               Khayyam nota alguma de energia, nenhuma
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">phrase</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">frase</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               de amor.
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">Aquella</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">Aquela</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               Sàki,
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                     <del rend="overtyped">que</del>
                     cuja
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">cuja</rdg>
               </app>
               figura
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">gracil</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">grácil</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               entrevista surge
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               (mas surge pouco) nos
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">rubayat</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">
                        <seg rendition="#i">rubbayat</seg>
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">
                        <seg rendition="#i">rubaiyat</seg>
                     </rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               , não é senão a "rapariga
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               que serve o vinho". O poeta é grato à sua
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">esvelteza</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">esbelteza</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               como
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               o
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">fôra</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">fora</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               à
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">esvelteza</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">esbelteza</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               da
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">amphora</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">ânfora</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               , onde o vinho se contives
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
               se.
               <app type="style">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">
                     <space dim="vertical" quantity="1" unit="minims" />
                  </rdg>
               </app>
            </p>
            <p>
               A alegria
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">falla</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">fala</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               <app type="punctuation">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC"/>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">,</rdg>
               </app>
               do vinho, como o Deão Aldrich:
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">---</rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">...</rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">(...)</rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z" />
               </app>
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z #Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                     <space dim="vertical" quantity="1" unit="minims" />
                  </rdg>
               </app>
            </p>
            <p>
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">
                     <space dim="horizontal" quantity="10" unit="minims" />A gente tem, a meu ver,
                     <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z" />
                     <space dim="horizontal" quantity="10" unit="minims" />Cinco razões para beber:
                     <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z" />
                     <space dim="horizontal" quantity="10" unit="minims" />Um brinde, um amigo, ou então
                     <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z" />
                     <space dim="horizontal" quantity="10" unit="minims" />Sede, ou poder vi-la ter,
                     <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z" />
                     <space dim="horizontal" quantity="10" unit="minims" />Ou qualquer outra razão.
                     <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z" /> 
                     <space dim="vertical" quantity="1" unit="minims" />                     
                  </rdg>
               </app>
               A
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">philosophia</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">filosofia</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">practica</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">prática</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               de Khayyam reduz-se pois a
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               um epicurismo suave, esbatido até ao
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">minimo</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">mínimo</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               do desejo de
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               prazer. Basta-lhe ver rosas e beber vinho. Uma brisa le
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
               ve, uma conversa sem
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                        <del rend="overtyped">inuito</del>
                        intuito
                     </rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">intuito</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               nem
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">proposito</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">propósito</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               , um
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">pucaro</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">púcaro</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               de vinho, flores,
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5">
                     <del rend="overtyped">em tanto põe</del>
                     em isso
                  </rdg>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">em isso</rdg>
               </app>
               , e em não
               <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               mais do que isso, põe o
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">sabio</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">sábio</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
               persa o seu desejo
               <app>
                  <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">maximo</rdg>
                     <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">máximo</rdg>
                  </rdgGrp>
               </app>
                .<lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
               <!-- em Zenith e Fonte não há quebra de parágrafo -->
               <app>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z #Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                      O amor agita e cansa, a acção dispersa e falha,
                      <app>
                          <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                              <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                                  ninguem
                                  <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
                              </rdg>
                              <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">ninguém</rdg>
                          </rdgGrp>
                      </app>
                      sabe saber e pensar embacia tudo. Mais vale pois cessar
                      <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
                      em nós de desejar ou de esperar, de ter a pretensão
                      <app>
                          <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                              <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                                  fu
                                  <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
                                  til
                              </rdg>
                              <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">fútil</rdg>
                          </rdgGrp>
                      </app>
                      de explicar o mundo, ou o
                      <app>
                          <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                              <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">proposito</rdg>
                              <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">propósito</rdg>
                          </rdgGrp>
                      </app>
                      estulto de o e
                      <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" type="hyphenated" break="no" />
                      mendar ou governar. Tudo é nada, ou, como se diz na
                      <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
                      <app type="style">
                          <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                             <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">Anthologia Grega</rdg>
                              <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">
                                 <seg rendition="#i">Antologia Grega</seg>
                              </rdg>
                             <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">Antologia Grega</rdg>
                          </rdgGrp>
                      </app>, "tudo vem da sem-razão", e é um grego,
                      <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
                      e portanto um racional, que o diz.
                      <lb ed="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5" />
                  
                  </rdg>
               </app>
            </p>
            <p>
               <app type="paragraph">
                  <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">
                     O amor agita e cansa, a acção dispersa e falha,
                     <app>
                        <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                              ninguem
   
                           </rdg>
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">ninguém</rdg>
                        </rdgGrp>
                     </app>
                     sabe saber e pensar embacia tudo. Mais vale pois cessar

                     em nós de desejar ou de esperar, de ter a pretensão
                     <app>
                        <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">
                              futil
                           </rdg>
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">fútil</rdg>
                        </rdgGrp>
                     </app>
                     de explicar o mundo, ou o
                     <app>
                        <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">proposito</rdg>
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">propósito</rdg>
                        </rdgGrp>
                     </app>
                     estulto de o emendar ou governar. Tudo é nada, ou, como se diz na
                     
                     <app>
                        <rdgGrp type="orthographic">
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.MS.Fr005a.5 #Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.C">Anthologia</rdg>
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.SC">
                              <seg rendition="#i">Antologia</seg>
                           </rdg>
                           <rdg wit="#Fr005.WIT.ED.CRIT.Z">Antologia</rdg>
                        </rdgGrp>
                     </app>
                     Grega, "tudo vem da sem-razão", e é um grego,
                     
                     e portanto um racional, que o diz.
                     
                  </rdg>
               </app>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
